doing such a ridiculous thing?

61
00:03:09,050 --> 00:03:09,890
Your Majesty.

62
00:03:10,730 --> 00:03:12,730
Yan Zhen has true love.

63
00:03:13,100 --> 00:03:14,770
Prime Minister Yan even

64
