133
00:05:41,860 --> 00:05:42,690
-Hua!
-Your Grace!

134
00:05:44,860 --> 00:05:46,250
Eunuch Wang.

135
00:05:47,220 --> 00:05:49,730
Please give them to His Majesty.

136
00:05:52,250 --> 00:05:54,930
