to tweak your ears off.

148
00:06:31,860 --> 00:06:35,100
I’ll cut your head and give it to her!

149
00:06:35,340 --> 00:06:37,300
I’m sorry, Your Majesty!

150
00:06:37,300 --> 00:06:38,020
Your Majesty.

151
00:06:38,300 --> 00:06:40,610
Prime Minister Yan has devoted himself
to our state for years.

152
