154
00:06:44,490 --> 00:06:47,100
But his merits equal demerits
and he doesn’t need to be executed.

155
00:06:47,660 --> 00:06:48,300
Your Majesty.

156
00:06:48,900 --> 00:06:50,810
Count Cheng’an made some sense.

157
00:06:51,730 --> 00:06:54,460
But we must put an end
to the dealing of official posts.

158
00:06:55,130 --> 00:06:57,900
